  <page>
    <title>Template:CreateFromTemplate</title>
    <revision>
      <model>wikitext</model>
      <format>text/x-wiki</format>
      <text>&lt;noinclude&gt;
Renders an inputbox for creating new pages from a template and lists pages previously created by this macro instance.

Parameters:
* preload - The template page to preload when creating a new page
* buttonlabel - Label for the create button
* macroid - Unique identifier for this macro instance (used to scope created pages)
&lt;/noinclude&gt;&lt;includeonly&gt;
{{#tag:inputbox|
type=create
preload={{{preload|preload}}}
preloadparams[]={{{macroid|}}}
buttonlabel={{{buttonlabel|Create from template}}}
width=28
break=no
useve=true
}}
{{#ask: [[Created by macro::{{{macroid|}}}]]
| format=embedded
| sort=Creation date
| order=desc
| limit=5
| searchlabel=More
}}
&lt;/includeonly&gt;
</text>
    </revision>
